\section{Physical and Number-Theoretic Interpretation}

The identical geometric ingredients (right conoid + 12 2I bridges + Dual-Zero regulator) that generate:
- Newton’s constant \(G_N\) (Paper 05/21),
- exactly three chiral generations and Yukawa hierarchies (Paper 20),
- the full bosonic Lagrangian (Paper 21),

also minimize the information action precisely when the Riemann Hypothesis holds. This reveals a deep unity between spacetime geometry, particle physics, and arithmetic.

We do not claim a classical analytic proof of the RH (still open), but a concrete geometric mechanism inside SAM3 that naturally selects the critical line as the physical vacuum.

